                     <interp inst="t17850914-59-off292" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17850914-59-cd293" type="crimeDate">23d day of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850914-59-off292 t17850914-59-cd293"></join> last, four saws, value 20 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17850914-59-victim670" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Jeffries
                  <interp inst="t17850914-59-victim670" type="surname" value="Jeffries"></interp>
